title: Stacey Abrams Concedes to Gov. Brian Kemp in Georgia
description: Ms. Abrams, a Democrat, bowed to Mr. Kemp, the Republican incumbent, in a rematch of their 2018 race. He had campaigned on his conservative policy wins.
dc:creator: Maya King

media:content.media:credit: Audra Melton for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Gov. Brian Kemp at a rally in Marietta, Ga., last week.
